{"tid":860517,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一個香港道具師，因假鈔做得太逼真，被判入獄","createTime":"2018-10-13T11:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T06:18:42.000Z","uid":74058,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"85c18acc47e7d45adad08a0458e30a533f5c5763","tid":860517,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"47歲的張偉全，是香港資深的道具製作人，圈內人稱&ldquo;道具全&rdquo;。入行29年，他參與了70多部電影的道具制作和場景策劃。今年5月31日，因管有22.3萬張拍戲時使用的道具鈔票，張偉全被指犯了&ldquo;保管僞制紙幣罪&rdquo;，判監四個月，緩刑兩年，事件震驚全香港。<br />\n<br />\nKeith Cheung, 47 years old, is an experienced Hong Kong prop person. In the past 29 years, he has made properties and planned scenes for more than 70 films. On May 31 this year, Keith was convicted of &quot;possession of counterfeit banknotes&quot;, sentenced to four months ' imprisonment with two years&rsquo; probation because of the possession of 223,000 pieces of prop banknotes. Hong Kong was shocked.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yl54qOOagCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyl54qOOagCs&d=fiBKki%2BMB0cRhTXjRDHmShxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=f2160bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yl54qOOagCs</a>"},{"pid":"125352dbc35ce5fb94b08bf4d7e93f3406dbfd1e","tid":860517,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"柒出國際"},{"pid":"9d0a7bc2105f8dd0459b7920e9a12eb0d0840d81","tid":860517,"uid":22095,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"一間話道具唔真嘅話 又話港產片唔認真㗎啦"},{"pid":"7ecc96aff6a933fbccbc32414dfa413b249f3221","tid":860517,"uid":10504,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:49:12.000Z","msg":"為左奶共 做埋D荒謬野柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254bab556abcd966c218142582235f64c74ed9b1","tid":860517,"uid":85946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10